Package: complexsurvey
Title: SBART Models for Clustered Complex Survey Data with Non-Gaussian Errors
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Abhishek", "Mandal",
                   email = "amandal2@fsu.edu",
                   role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fits Soft Bayesian Additive Regression Trees (SBART) for
    clustered complex survey data with subject-specific weights and
    non-Gaussian errors. Implements skew-normal, skew-t, and quantile
    regression models as described in Mandal et al. (2025)
    <doi:10.1080/10485252.2025.2574708>.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports:
    SoftBart,
    invgamma,
    truncnorm,
    sn,
    glmnet,
    extraDistr,
    ald,
    loo,
    diversitree
